profile:
Poshployees: Attentive & Trustworthy
Posh is able to provide the trustworthiness & personable service of an independent/solo cleaning lady, while still upholding the reliability & expertise of an established company. After many years of recruiting, training, and keeping genuinely great people, Posh has built a team of Home Cleaning Staff who can consistently provide outstanding Quality of Service.

Servicing Hamilton, Ancaster, Stoney Creek, Dundas, Burlington, Oakville, Waterdown, Grimsby, Beamsville, Milton and Binbrook, Posh Cleaning provides maid service for your home with integrity and reliability. Just imagine opening your door to find a spotless house - we promise to remove the burden of cleaning from your housekeeping – freeing up your time to focus on the more important things in life!
 
We are happy to provide you with references from our current clients :)
services:
• Weekly, Bi-Weekly or 4-Week Recurring Cleaning Service.

• Spring Cleaning – any time of year!

• Move-In/ Move-Out Service for when you are relocating.

• Post-Construction or Post-Renovation Clean Up.

• Cleaning for Home Staging to improve the perceived value when you are selling.
brands:
Professional & Brand-Name Supplies

State of the art cleaning techniques according to industry best practices. We are official cleaning nerds!
specialities: • Cleaning for all types of homes; from apartments and condominiums to single family homes of all sizes, and rental properties.
